  "question_text": "<div class=\"paragraph\">The athletic director of a large university is curious about community opinion of a new initiative to open a sports arena for both community members and college students to use. The cost of this initiative will be funded through a county-wide sales tax.  </div><div class=\"paragraph\">The athletic director went to several different health clubs and asked members there if they would support the initiative. Out of <span class=\"tex2jax_process\"><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-7695-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>500</mn></math>\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size: 114%; position: relative;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-35466\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-35467\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-35468\" class=\"mjx-mn\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.387em; padding-bottom: 0.387em;\">500</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>500</mn></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-7695\">500</script></span> people surveyed, <span class=\"tex2jax_process\"><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-7696-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>374</mn></math>\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size: 114%; position: relative;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-35469\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-35470\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-35471\" class=\"mjx-mn\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.387em; padding-bottom: 0.387em;\">374</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>374</mn></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-7696\">374</script></span> said they would support the sports arena.  </div><div class=\"paragraph\">What is a type of bias present here? Furthermore, is the true population proportion who support this initiative higher, lower, or about the same as the sample proportion?</div>",
